Bash script using YAD (Yet Another Dialog) to install, update, uninstall and
search for, Flatpaks. Manually update Appstream data. Uses translations. Opens
HTML page from Appstream catalog when row double clicked, except for search.
Command terminal used to execute Flatpak command for selected Flatpaks.

Works on Fedora 37 and 38 LXQt.
Requires yad and flatpak.
